Meet The Team

Our team includes nurses, physicians, software engineers, and data analysits.

Jay Feldman

Chief Medical Officer

Jay Feldman, MD is a Front-Line Emergency Medicine Physician at Memorial Regional Hospital–a Level I Trauma center in South Florida. He earned his medical degree from the prestigious Sackler School of Medicine–New York / Tel Aviv curriculum. His Emergency Medicine Residency training was achieved at the high acuity University Medical Center of Las Vegas, NV. He is certified by the American Board of Emergency Medicine.

A seasoned physician with leadership experience in academic and clinical medicine, Dr. Feldman is an Assistant Professor at Florida Atlantic University, Florida International University, Nova Southeastern University, and the University of Connecticut. He is the Director of South Beach MD and a co-founder of Miami Beach MD consulting services, specializing in concierge services, healthcare operations, and medical education.
